response.overview: On September 16th GCW in Liverpool 2023 is live on FITE+ straight from Hangar 34. The event features the GCW World Title Match where Blake Christian defends his title against Leon Slater.  Also in the lineup:  Non Title Match  Rina Yamashita vs Session Moth Martina  Tag Team Match  Jimmy Lloyd & Starboy Charlie vs CPF (Danny Black & Joe Lando)  Gringo Loco vs Arez  Six Man Tag Team Match  Thrussy (Allie Katch, Dark Sheik & Effy) vs James Ellis, Mulligan & Tate Mayfairs  Non Title Match  Jordan Oliver vs Man Like DeReiss  Joey Janela vs Blue Kane  Tony Deppen vs Masha Slamovich  Tag Team Death Match  Big Joe & Clint Margera vs Los Macizos (Ciclope & Miedo Extremo)
response.title: GCW in Liverpool 2023
